00:19.853 --> 00:21.055
[ Rap music continues ]

00:21.089 --> 00:22.323
We're arriving in Brazil

00:22.356 --> 00:24.192
at the peak
of Carnival season,

00:24.225 --> 00:27.361
one of the most sexually
liberated parties on the planet,

00:27.395 --> 00:30.264
to explore a country
whose relationship

00:30.298 --> 00:34.102
with the queer community
is complex and often extreme.

00:34.135 --> 00:37.071
It's a country with some of the
most progressive equality laws

00:37.105 --> 00:38.672
in Latin America,

00:38.706 --> 00:43.644
but also has the highest LGBTQ
murder rate in the world.

00:43.677 --> 00:46.447
So Ian and I are here
to explore what's going on,

00:46.480 --> 00:49.250
and what it's really like
to be queer in Brazil.

00:51.252 --> 00:55.723
**

