07:07.194 --> 07:09.563
PAGE:
Despite his optimism,

07:09.597 --> 07:13.534
the world outside the
celebration is somewhat harsher.

07:13.567 --> 07:16.136
Just a few weeks
before we got here,

07:16.169 --> 07:20.007
the dead body of 25-year-old
transwoman Piu de Silva,

07:20.040 --> 07:22.510
one of Carnival's
most prominent dancers,

07:22.543 --> 07:25.145
seen here in costume,
was found tortured and shot

07:25.178 --> 07:26.814
in a favela near her home.

07:26.847 --> 07:29.149
No arrests have been made
in the case,

07:29.182 --> 07:33.120
and the exact motive is unclear,
but many suspect transphobia.

07:33.153 --> 07:35.823
De Silva is just one
of the growing number

07:35.856 --> 07:37.925
of transgender victims
in Brazil,

07:37.958 --> 07:40.093
a country
with the greatest number

07:40.127 --> 07:42.596
of murdered transpeople
in the world.

07:42.630 --> 07:45.633
Carnival is
an over-the-top extravaganza

07:45.666 --> 07:48.502
and feels very accepting
of everyone.

07:48.536 --> 07:50.704
But in speaking to locals later,

07:50.738 --> 07:53.807
the world outside can feel
very different.

08:19.567 --> 08:21.835
