on the planet winds down,

08:24.572 --> 08:26.173
it's gonna be interesting to see

08:26.206 --> 08:28.241
how Carnival compares
to daily life

08:28.275 --> 08:31.945
for the queer community
here in Rio.

08:38.285 --> 08:42.155
While in town, I'm meeting
my friend Ana Rezende

08:42.189 --> 08:43.824
from the band CSS.

08:43.857 --> 08:45.926
She was born and raised here,

08:45.959 --> 08:49.997
